data.description: This beautiful 2500+ sq ft, traditional 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is packed with upgraded features and offers a spacious 2 car garage. High end LPV floors greet you inside that cover the entire 1st floor. A formal dining room shares a foyer with window views of the covered front porch. The spacious open living room allows for tons of natural light with windows overlooking the backyard and gas fireplace. The kitchen offers energy star appliances and granite countertops. Both upstairs full bathrooms are paired with marbled features. Continuing to the shaded backyard, there's an East facing patio provides cool afternoon summers. This home sits on a generous lot surrounded by acres of woods towards the back and adjacent side yard in a comforting quiet cul-de-sac. Come make this house your home today! *sqft., lot size, schools, restrictions, are important, Buyer is responsible to verify.*
